column5: Well Ronnie and I got out so here is a tease from today it was a great day out on LSC I went out two times for a couple quick fishes and stayed away from the heat of the day       Hope to get a full report and videos done tomorrow or monday
Nice Fish Mike... It was tough at my end of the lake!
wow, that thing is thick lol
And what a tease it is Mike Cant wait to see the fulll report
Sure does look thick. Show me more show me more.
Wow, you do great down there guys!

Sorry to say but the report will have to wait.  Oh yeah these two were small compared to the two we got today what a great weekend two monster fish days in a row and the wife and I are heading back out right now hope to have a report tomorrow maybe another tease tonight musky rock.  BTW sorry team 10 I did not have the sign ready for any of the big girls to come
Nice!  Did you have your sign Mike.
Yes but I did not use it but I did tonight and upped our points.
Mike-one can tell from your reports over the last 2 seasons that LSC is definitely on a momentum swing. Great for you and whoever fishes there.
Love seeing your reports Mike. Those fish look real thick!
Today I had a couple special guests out with me it was a amazing day here is anotehr tease just two of them the rest is for the report some time
